Gaudi conceived this church in 1912 , though it was n't until 1920 that they started to build it .
Since the beginning , the work was interrupted in different periods and started again .
After Gaudi 's death it was a critical stop which was fortunately solved three years later .
Nowadays , hard work is being done in order to finish as soon as possible .
The visitor can wander around the building or follow a guided visit .
